dc_description_s: These data layers represent wetlands for Calumet County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase 'Calumet_Wetlands_2018.gdb'. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are 'Wetlands2Acre' and 'WetlandsArea'. [Wetlands for Calumet County, WI. The data layer is in Wisconsin Transverse Mercator (WTM) projection system, North American Datum 1983 with the 1991 adjustments.]
uw_supplemental_s: For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: http://www.calumetmaps.com/data.html
